rwissenschaftliche Historisierung der RAF vor.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aTerrorismzGermanyvHistoriography. 0aTerrorismzGermanyxHistoriography. 4aDeutsche Geschichte. 4aErinnerung. 4aGermanistik. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichte. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aLiteratur. 4aMediengeschichte. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aRAF. 4aTerrorismus. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aGerman History.  aGerman Literature.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aLiterature.  aMedia History.  aMedia Studies.  aTerrorism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013z978311037074408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2013z9783110401219oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383762390140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839423905?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839423905423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839423905/original  a978-3-11-037074-4  transcript Highlight Collection Lit. & Kultur 2010-2013c2010d2013  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TGPb2013  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013